<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11928</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15789</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这是一个寒冷的早晨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15789</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19348</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几个人聚在墓地里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19348</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22891</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小镇的磨坊主死了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22891</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27064</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>磨坊主的三个儿子站在墓边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27064</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36331</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们的名字是弗朗西斯、巴蒂斯塔和卡拉巴斯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36331</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41000</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会想父亲的。” 弗朗西斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41000</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴蒂斯塔点点头。“我也是。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56088</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡拉巴斯擦了擦眼泪。“愿他安息。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56088</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60648</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>兄弟们来到了磨坊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60648</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64533</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“父亲很穷。” 巴蒂斯塔说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64533</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67834</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他只有磨坊和驴。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67834</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72096</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要磨坊。” 弗朗西斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72096</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75346</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么？” 巴蒂斯塔大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75346</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78565</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我最大。” 弗朗西斯说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78565</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82887</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我来接手父亲的事业。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82887</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90200</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我要磨面粉赚钱。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90200</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98890</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那我要驴。” 巴蒂斯塔说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98890</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105206</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我用它把货物运到市场去。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105206</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109246</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们合作吧。” 弗朗西斯说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109246</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113593</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我磨面粉，你运到市场去。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113593</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118424</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴蒂斯塔笑了。“好！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118424</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123008</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那我呢？” 卡拉巴斯小声问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123008</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128819</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴蒂斯塔耸耸肩。“父亲没有其他东西了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128819</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133397</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那我什么都得不到了？” 卡拉巴斯问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133397</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135928</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这不公平。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135928</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143573</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>弗朗西斯耸耸肩。“你最小啊。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143573</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150280</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，一只猫扑向了老鼠。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150280</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153387</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦！” 巴蒂斯塔说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153387</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156910</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我忘记父亲的猫——普斯了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156910</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160207</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>弗朗西斯咧嘴笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160207</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163871</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“卡拉巴斯，普斯就给你吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163871</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169191</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们俩哈哈大笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169191</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180399</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡拉巴斯叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>